text: Virginia McGrath (born 13 March 1965) is an Irish equestrian. She competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Irish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from London
